title: Grateful Dead Live at San Francisco Civic Auditorium on 1987-01-30
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Minglewood Blues, Candyman, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, When Push Comes To Shove, Beat It On Down The Line-> Promised Land-> China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider

Set 2

Iko Iko-> Women Are Smarter, Ship of Fools, Estimated Prophet-> Truckin'-> Drums-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Brokedown Palace

reviews.review_text:
Classic Oade Tape Show is middling other than the Estimated, and post-Space, but it is a wonderful Oade FOB. 
3.5 for show
5 for sound
